Class ExtensionQueryService

java.lang.Object
  com.vmware.vcloud.sdk.QueryService
      com.vmware.vcloud.sdk.admin.AdminQueryService
          com.vmware.vcloud.sdk.admin.extensions.ExtensionQueryService

public class ExtensionQueryService
extends AdminQueryService

This class provides methods to build and run the generalized and specialized queries. All the queries can be run by a system admin.

Since:
API 1.5, SDK 1.5
Author:
Ecosystem Engineering.
